Slackware Current Repository by Conraid

======================================================================

chisel (A fast TCP/UDP tunnel over HTTP)

Chisel is a fast TCP/UDP tunnel, transported over HTTP, secured via
SSH. Single executable including both client and server. Written in
Go. Chisel is mainly useful for passing through firewalls, though it
can also be used to provide a secure endpoint into your network.

HOME: https://github.com/jpillora/chisel

